OL,4,Ctax claim - so who is right?
OL,6,FThe Tories have doubled down on the
OL,7,FLabour tax claim despite the fact a
OL,8,Fletter from the top Treasury civil
OL,9,Fservant undermines the figure, ITV
OL,10,FNews Economics Editor Joel Hills and
OL,11,FPolitical Editor Robert Peston discuss
OL,13,FThe UK's official statistics regulator
OL,14,Fhas launched an investigation into
OL,15,FRishi Sunak's claims that Sir Keir
OL,16,FStarmer will increase taxes by #2,000
OL,17,Fper household, which Labour has
OL,18,Frefuted.
