OL,6,FMr Sunak's claim was one of the hot
OL,7,Ftopics of his Tuesday night . He
OL,8,Frepeated several times that Labour's
OL,9,Fpolicies will be funded at the expense
OL,10,Fof a tax uplift for working families -
OL,11,Fsomething Sir Keir called "absolute
OL,12,Fgarbage".
