OL,6,FIt has descended into a bitter row,
OL,7,Fwith Labour calling on Mr Sunak to
OL,8,Fcorrect the record after he
OL,9,F"embarrassingly" got the sum wrong and
OL,10,Ftoday launching a social media
OL,11,Fcampaign calling him and the Tories
OL,12,F"liars". Meanwhile, Mr Sunak and his
OL,13,Fparty continue to double down on the
OL,14,Ftax claim.
OL,16,FHowever, a leaked letter from the
OL,17,FTreasury's senior official casts
OL,18,Ffurther doubt on the prime minister's
OL,19,Fstatement.
