OL,6,FThe Office for Statistics Regulation
OL,7,Fhas confirmed it is looking into the
OL,8,Fuse of the #2,000 figure.
OL,10,FSo, who is right?
OL,12,FWhere has the #2,000 figure come from?
OL,14,FLabour has not said it has plans to
OL,15,Fincrease a working household's tax by
OL,16,F#2,000.
