OL,6,FIt is understood the figure is based
OL,7,Fon an estimate produced by the
OL,8,FConservative Party - which the Labour
OL,9,FParty disputes - and would be spread
OL,10,Fover four years.
OL,12,FInitial analysis by charityalso said
OL,13,Fthe prime minister's claim was based
OL,14,Fon Conservative estimates of Labour
OL,15,Fspending plans and covers a long list
OL,16,Fof policy announcements.
OL,18,FRishi Sunak repeatedly made the claim
OL,19,Fduring the debate
