OL,6,FHowever, the Treasury's senior
OL,7,Fofficial has urged ministers - in a
OL,8,Fletter leaked to media - not to
OL,9,Fattribute the Tories' claim that
OL,10,FLabour's policies would cost #38.5
OL,11,Fbillion to civil servants. This
OL,12,Ftherefore casts doubt on the tax claim.
OL,14,FIn a letter dated June 3, Treasury
OL,15,FPermanent Secretary James Bowler said
OL,16,Fthe calculation "includes costs beyond
OL,17,Fthose provided by the Civil Service".
