OL,7,Fclaim several times during the
OL,8,Fshowdown, Sir Keir finally called the
OL,9,Fclaim "absolute garbage" and clapped
OL,10,Fback: "What's happened here is they
OL,11,Fput in pretend Labour policies to the
OL,12,FTreasury and then they get a false
OL,13,Freadout.
OL,15,F"What they've put in for this analysis
OL,16,Fis a mental health policy that isn't
OL,17,Fthe Labour Party's policy, he's put in
OL,18,Fone of his own policies. He's asked
OL,19,Fthe civil service to cost it.
